Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.78,0:00:15.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,My right hand holds a bowl of gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.46,0:00:19.79,Opening,,0,0,0,,And my left holds one of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.79,0:00:24.46,Opening,,0,0,0,,Never one without the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:37.62,Opening,,0,0,0,,Two unseen bowls for each of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:45.98,Opening,,0,0,0,,The golden one is filled with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:53.37,Opening,,0,0,0,,shining warmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:57.99,Opening,,0,0,0,,Since we met, my golden bowl
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.99,0:01:05.18,Opening,,0,0,0,,cannot hold all my happiness and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:15.32,Opening,,0,0,0,,Golden joy, silver sadness,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:22.66,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would leave my past behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:27.40,Opening,,0,0,0,,For you, for the sake of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:34.34,Opening,,0,0,0,,I would empty the bowls of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, is this a little too childish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it is cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take this, and the same for Nanako too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Matching pajamas!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.84,0:02:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be sewing pajamas next week in home economics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo Nanako-san, I've told you about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you! I am Shinobu Mariko, Nanako's classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to stop by on a Sunday without calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have something I wanted to show Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu Mariko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nanako is out seeing a movie with her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Arikura Tomoko-san is her friend's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what was is it that came between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably because you've gotten too popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.40,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Mariko Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko Shinobu likes you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She really adores you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And everyone wants you to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I... sometimes she scares me a little....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,8. I Want You
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:52.17,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Seiran School, next stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A test, first period! That teacher is a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall asleep during the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The real me is wide awake... but perhaps not my brain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko, we can go home together today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.20,0:04:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you Misonoo-san is no longer the Misonoo-san you knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand Nanako is Nanako no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say... or make up... I understand her well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...because I've known her since we were both little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.79,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get back together with Misonoo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I won't let go of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't let go of Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.87,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing? Class is starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...Misonoo-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Good morning, Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,First period is Literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:09.42,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Surprised by my footsteps, the face turned back towards me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:13.09,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Being an untalented poet, I cannot express well enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:17.06,Default-Alt2,,0,0,0,,Those dewy eyes! Those deep, shining eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to talk to you later. Something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.82,0:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, next Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have a little party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I really want you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to, that's ok. In fact, I'll understand if no one comes at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...since it is a party for the daughter of a pornographer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that! I never thought of you that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, you'll come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? For sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come? Terrific! Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited! I have to tell my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's next Saturday at six at the Hotel Royale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yor are crushing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I rented "The Rose Room".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Rose Room"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san, thank you! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What an impudent girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She is going to stay in the Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki-san, you'd better come up with something new!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I have some new ideas...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki Aya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you come to the Sorority house now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Miya-sama is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the Sorority House!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for her being chosen, then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry to trouble you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your impression of our Sorority House?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful! It's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I've adored it ever since Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...that there were times when members left the Sorority...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.11,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we accepted new members from the freshmen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then... I still have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No. There is no chance that you will be chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you already know why not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I give you fair warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't become a victim of your own device.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd not only lose your chance to become a Sorority member...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you would forever face the hostility of the entire Sorority.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Tomoko so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoko! It must be Tomoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry, I'm not Tomoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about this Saturday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... your friend's birthday party?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can wear the dress your father bought you the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering what to bring for a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,For you to agree to go to Mariko's party is hard enough in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you're even baking cookies for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is it helping me bake these cookies? You should talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! I want to make them with lots of salt and tabasco!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what are you going to give to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? And when is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fabulous...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A birthday party... Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever could be coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... excuse me, where is "The Rose Room"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be Miss Misonoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Shinobu is expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you would come this way, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.70,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored to be invited today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.51,0:13:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You did come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy Birthday! I am honored...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out! Come over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...and meet my Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu-san is so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially beautiful, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you! Mariko has told me so much about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you! I'm Misonoo Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She talks about you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy you and Mariko have become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all! It's my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.86,0:14:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will be a blessing to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Too many formalities! Let's eat instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko, why don't you blow out your candles?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But will I be able to blow out all 16 of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead and eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like caviar? What about some wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.14,0:14:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...where are all the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.24,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one I invited!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You rented this... this enormous room...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Until last year, it was only Mom and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.95,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody would come if I invited them anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my father would remain in his study, working...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing special...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Can I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Mom, cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You baked these yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.06,0:16:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They look delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They look so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a good cook, Misonoo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like... I didn't really know much at all... about Mariko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm glad I came after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very grateful for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...and for all the things you did for me, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.36,0:17:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...thank you for bringing me home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all, it was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you that made the party special.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was our pleasure, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.58,0:17:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My house is right here... I'd like to show it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't want to impose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! No imposition at all, right Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! It's a bit sudden but Nanako would be very welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok? Ok? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok. Just for a little while...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn around, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, these are delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really good at baking cookies!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here's some coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want Cafe Royale, with brandy, or cafe-au-lait?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, regular coffee is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san, could I stop by and bring you some pies?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you pity me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If so... no thank you, I'm content as-is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... I do very much appreciate your kind heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.41,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.48,0:19:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please, come by anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, would you like to take a bath with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! Don't friends do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You do that with Tomoko, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.84,0:19:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your back is simply marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skin is so clear and pale!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop staring at my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I like all beautiful things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I like my body, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just between you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I gaze into the mirror for hours and hours
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...admiring the beauty of my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What I really want is to be grown-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be grown-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt, Mariko's breasts are much bigger than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like a beautiful rosebud, waiting to bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it's really late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko-san, I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you mustn't! Please stay overnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's raining, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will be ok for you to stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've stayed overnight with Tomoko, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Good friends do that, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I wasn't planning on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad will be worried if I don't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ok! I'll just call your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So please, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come another time, when I have permission from my mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mariko! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you can't! I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious, I'll kill you and then myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.64,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.52,0:22:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.99,0:22:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely will not let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.06,0:22:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up! Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.53,0:22:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stay away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.78,0:22:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you! Your friend is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.34,0:22:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko, what on earth is the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait! Don't go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go home! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.76,0:22:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you going? Isn't it ok to just stay overnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.46,0:23:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What! How can you say that? This isn't "friends"....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.02,0:23:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, get a hold of yourself! Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.33,0:23:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go! I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.12,0:23:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Mariko!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! Help me Mom! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.05,0:23:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My Brother!...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Snow white...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind went blank...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything around was white... I kept running.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.95,0:23:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.08,0:23:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain was so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:14.18,Ending,,0,0,0,,I dreamed I was chasing a rainbow...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:19.65,Ending,,0,0,0,,Then the rainbow I was chasing was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.12,0:24:25.26,Ending,,0,0,0,,Before, I had no strength, no will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.26,0:24:30.73,Ending,,0,0,0,,But now because of you, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.46,0:24:37.00,Ending,,0,0,0,,Feelings of love, like raindrops
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:42.48,Ending,,0,0,0,,Come pouring from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:45.21,Ending,,0,0,0,,This is surely a game
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.21,0:24:48.01,Ending,,0,0,0,,Of some mischievous fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.01,0:24:50.42,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always dancing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.42,0:24:55.69,Ending,,0,0,0,,Always capricious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.56,0:25:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, Kaoru-no-Kimi again suffers from her recurring chest pains.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.92,0:25:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Searching for medicine, Nanako goes to Rei for help...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.13,0:25:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Rei seems ambivalent and unresponsive...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.97,0:25:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So Nanako slaps her!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.99,0:25:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode: Relapse!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.88,0:25:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, Dear Brother... There is no end to my tears...
